    <title>Reddit’s upgraded AMA posts are rolling out this week</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="The Reddit logo over an orange and black background" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/beCM9EApDHBm53b5myzwtw3v8-o=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73505657/acastro_STK024_02.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;Illustration by Alex Castro / The Verge&lt;/figcaption&gt;
